{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523150/extras/Baza_Pod_DO_GIFA.gif?t=1729592494\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">IMMERSE YOURSELF INTO THE WORLD OF THE FLAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How much can you take, until you snap? The Flat is a first-person action game set within the dark and grotesque walls of Corpo Corporation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You step into the role of a gray worker, just another cog in the corporate machine. Try to understand the twisted logic that powers this dystopian nightmare and use it to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523150/extras/Hero_VS_Enons.gif?t=1729592494\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you snap? Will you send the boss on a wild goose chase with a fake memo or perhaps 'accidentally' trigger a cascade of events that leads to an office massacre? Your choice, your mayhem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523150/extras/Gif_Minigra.gif?t=1729592494\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Step into a vibrant and dynamic world, bustling with characters living out their daily schedules.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Engage in high-octane combat that's as dynamic as you are. Use your surroundings for strategic advantage and turn the tides in your favor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Dive into a unique stealth mechanic\u2014your goal isn't to hide, but to pretend to work. How well can you blen